{"tid":2337642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔女, 可唔可以教下我, 點樣喺SweetRing溝女?","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T18:21:20.000Z","uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a21a5eedf69d93dea3152885c0c17617a1ccdb26","tid":2337642,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗我嘅幸福著想, 教我應該點做.<br />\n有個女仔佢係對我向右畫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6qptWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6qptWa.png&h=d2b29dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對我嚟講應該係兄妹戀, 因為佢細過我<br />\n<br />\n另一個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsia8Y8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbsia8Y8.png&h=95f28540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我撳咗之後, 佢就搵我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ANrHjj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ANrHjj.png&h=04f62eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該係姐弟戀, 因為佢大過我<br />\n<br />\n我點樣回應佢哋好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打好心講畀我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!"},{"pid":"cedfcc3975ab09816288f4234ad90fb258c25a76","tid":2337642,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f132ac4c941049b6f455a4c7d028ab885d5e44bb","tid":2337642,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢嚟㗎"},{"pid":"b64b514eb8776a0c8818b37edc525167bbc14a16","tid":2337642,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-